hiveArticle.title: ColorChallenge - Friday Blue - Swimming Pool
hiveArticle.body:
My entry for today's #colorchallenge is a swimming pool where kids are enjoying. I tried to capture the running kid and his jump onto the swimming pool. But since my mobile camera does not support multiple at once I missed a frame in between.

![IMG_20171105_112219.jpg](https://res.cloudinary.com/hpiynhbhq/image/upload/v1510317599/yequqfsti7tg5es4crgs.jpg)

![IMG_20171105_112221.jpg](https://res.cloudinary.com/hpiynhbhq/image/upload/v1510317573/o0w4dbyiqpleeht2y7kj.jpg)
